<td colspan="2" class="" style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/classic/tripods/index.shtml" class="external text" title="http://www.bbc.co.uk/cult/classic/tripods/index.shtml" rel="nofollow">Official website</a></td>
